<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2409] edismax unescaped colon returns no results</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2409</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The edismax query parser should behave OK when a colon is in the query, but does not refer to a field name.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
